---
# Clang-tidy configuration for Otium OS
# Enforces coding standards for the unikernel architecture

Checks: >
  cppcoreguidelines-avoid-non-const-global-variables

CheckOptions:
  - key: cppcoreguidelines-avoid-non-const-global-variables.AllowInternalLinkage
    value: false

# Global variables (both static and non-static) break process isolation
# in the unikernel model where multiple process instances share the same
# address space.
